query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(site pl) NoHashJoin(pl q1 site tag tq1 tq2 c1) NoHashJoin(c1 pl q1 site tag tq1 tq2 q2) */ select count(q1.id)
from site AS site
inner join post_link AS pl
on pl.site_id = site.site_id AND site.site_name = 'german'
inner join question AS q1
on pl.site_id = q1.site_id AND pl.post_id_from = q1.id
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on tq1.site_id = q1.site_id AND tq1.question_id = q1.id
inner join tag AS tag
on tag.site_id = pl.site_id AND tag.id = tq1.tag_id AND tag.site_id = tq1.site_id AND tag.site_id = tq1.site_id AND tag.name IN ('objective-c',
'.net',
'css')
inner join tag_question AS tq2
on tag.id = tq2.tag_id
inner join comment AS c1
on c1.site_id = q1.site_id AND c1.post_id = q1.id
inner join question AS q2
on tq2.site_id = q2.site_id AND tq2.question_id = q2.id AND pl.site_id = q2.site_id AND pl.post_id_to = q2.id
inner join comment AS c2
on c2.site_id = q2.site_id AND c2.post_id = q2.id AND c1.date < c2.date;
